name: WWE NXT UK
overview: A professional wrestling program showcasing the best of WWE's UK division.

episodes.name: NXT UK 01
episodes.overview: On the first episode of NXT UK, Pete Dunne defends his WWE United Kingdom Title against Noam Dar. Plus, Toni Storm and others in action!

episodes.name: NXT UK 02
episodes.overview: Tyler Bate goes one-on-one with Wolfgang in the main event. Plus, Zack Gibson speaks out, Killer Kelly battles Dakota Kai, and more!

episodes.name: NXT UK 03
episodes.overview: Noam Dar and Zack Gibson look to settle their explosive rivalry in the main event. Plus, Trent Seven takes on Saxon Huxley, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT UK 04
episodes.overview: Mark Andrews battles Wolfgang in an exciting main event, Sam Gradwell and Saxon Huxley take on Moustache Mountain, and more!

episodes.name: NXT UK 05
episodes.overview: Danny Burch challenges Pete Dunne for the WWE United Kingdom Championship. Wolfgang and The Coffey Brothers make an emphatic statement.

episodes.name: NXT UK 06
episodes.overview: Mark Andrews, Flash Morgan and Ashton Smith combat Wolfgang and The Coffey Brothers in the main event. Trent Seven confronts Zack Gibson.

episodes.name: NXT UK 07
episodes.overview: A brand-new championship is unveiled to the world. Wolfgang looks to assert his dominance in the main event. Tyler Bate faces Ashton Smith.

episodes.name: NXT UK 08
episodes.overview: The tournament to crown the NXT UK Women's Champion begins with two exciting bouts. A brawl breaks out when Trent Seven faces Zack Gibson.

episodes.name: NXT UK 09
episodes.overview: The tournament to crown the first NXT UK Women's Champion continues with Xia Brookside, Rhea Ripley, Isla Dawn and Toni Storm in action!

episodes.name: NXT UK 10
episodes.overview: The tournament to crown the first NXT UK Women's Champion reaches the Semifinals with Toni Storm, Dakota Kai, and more in action!

episodes.name: NXT UK 11
episodes.overview: Jordan Devlin challenges Pete Dunne for the WWE UK Championship. Millie McKenzie and Xia Brookside take on Charlie Morgan and Killer Kelly.

episodes.name: NXT UK 12
episodes.overview: The tournament to crown the first-ever NXT United Kingdom Women's Champion concludes with Rhea Ripley and Toni Storm battling for the gold.

episodes.name: NXT UK 13
episodes.overview: The returning Travis Banks confronts Wolfgang and his allies. Flash Morgan Webster takes on Jordan Devlin in the main event.

episodes.name: NXT UK 14
episodes.overview: Travis Banks and Wolfgang face each other in a main event showdown. Plus, Rhea Ripley, Ligero and many more in action!

episodes.name: NXT UK 15
episodes.overview: Trent Seven and Joe Coffey take to the ring to settle their problems. Plus, Killer Kelly, James Drake and more!

episodes.name: NXT UK 16
episodes.overview: Eddie Dennis and 'Bomber' Dave Mastiff meet in a hard-hitting main event. Zack Gibson and James Drake make their intentions known.

episodes.name: NXT UK 17
episodes.overview: The NXT UK Women's Championship is on the line, as Rhea Ripley defends her title against Isla Dawn. Plus, Moustache Mountain and more!

episodes.name: NXT UK 18
episodes.overview: While continuing to call out Pete Dunne, Joe Coffey gears up for the main-event action. Fabian Aichner interferes in a tag team match.

episodes.name: NXT UK 19
episodes.overview: During a special announcement by NXT UK General Manager Johnny Saint, Toni Storm seizes an opportunity to further her in-ring career.

episodes.name: NXT UK 20
episodes.overview: Deonna Purrazzo challenges Rhea Ripley for the NXT UK Women's Championship in the main event. Eddie Dennis sends a message to Dave Mastiff.

episodes.name: NXT UK 21
episodes.overview: Joe Coffey and WWE UK Champion Pete Dunne continue their explosive rivalry during a tag team match between Gallus and Moustache Mountain.

episodes.name: NXT UK 22
episodes.overview: Physicality breaks out when WWE UK Champion Pete Dunne and Joe Coffey meet to sign the contract for their upcoming match.

episodes.name: NXT UK 23
episodes.overview: Gallus send a message to anyone who stands in their way. Jinny makes her intentions known. Mark Andrews and Flash Morgan Webster unite.

episodes.name: NXT UK 24
episodes.overview: As NXT UK TakeOver: Blackpool approaches, British Strong Style battle all three members of Gallus in a Six-Man Tag Team Match main event.

episodes.name: NXT UK 26
episodes.overview: See exclusive matches from Blackpool, including Mark Andrews and Flash Morgan Webster taking on Fabian Aichner and Marcel Barthel.

episodes.name: NXT UK 27
episodes.overview: Pete Dunne comes face-to-face with a new threat to his WWE United Kingdom Championship. Travis Banks faces Jordan Devlin in the main event.

episodes.name: NXT UK 28
episodes.overview: WALTER makes his in-ring debut against Jack Starz. Also, Zack Gibson and James Drake learn of new challengers to the NXT UK Tag Team Titles.

episodes.name: February 06, 2019
episodes.overview: WALTER continues to live up to his reputation in a main event battle against Gallus' Mark Coffey. Rhea Ripley takes out her frustrations.

episodes.name: February 13, 2019
episodes.overview: A verbal confrontation between Toni Storm and Rhea Ripley erupts in physicality. Pete Dunne faces Wolfgang in the main event.

episodes.name: February 20, 2019
episodes.overview: Rhea Ripley challenges Toni Storm for the NXT UK Women's Championship in the main event. Danny Burch and Oney Lorcan arrive.

episodes.name: February 27, 2019
episodes.overview: Danny Burch and Oney Lorcan challenge The Grizzled Young Veterans for the NXT UK Tag Team Titles in the main event.

episodes.name: March 06, 2019
episodes.overview: The main event sees Travis Banks and Jordan Devlin battle it out in a Falls Count Anywhere Match.

episodes.name: March 13, 2019
episodes.overview: WALTER and WWE United Kingdom Champion Pete Dunne take on Mark and Joe Coffey in the main event. Noam Dar returns with a new attitude.

episodes.name: March 20, 2019
episodes.overview: Pete Dunne lets everyone know who he wants to defend his WWE United Kingdom Championship against at NXT TakeOver: New York.

episodes.name: March 27, 2019
episodes.overview: WALTER and Pete Dunne meet face-to-face to sign the contract for their upcoming match for the WWE United Kingdom Championship.

episodes.name: April 3, 2019
episodes.overview: The Grizzled Young Veterans address the challengers for their NXT UK Tag Team Titles. Trent Seven faces Joe Coffey in the main event.

episodes.name: April 10, 2019
episodes.overview: Jinny challenges Toni Storm for the NXT UK Women's Championship in the main event. Plus, Piper Niven takes to the ring to face Killer Kelly.

episodes.name: April 17, 2019
episodes.overview: Kenny Williams and Amir Jordan face The Grizzled Young Veterans in the main event, while Rhea Ripley targets Kacy Catanzaro.

episodes.name: April 24, 2019
episodes.overview: Toni Storm makes a vow. Kay Lee Ray battles Xia Brookside. Moustache Mountain faces Flash Morgan Webster and Mark Andrews in the main event.

episodes.name: May 1, 2019
episodes.overview: A WWE United Kingdom Champion WALTER faces Jordan Devlin in the main event, Pete Dunne demands a rematch for the title he lost.

episodes.name: May 8, 2019
episodes.overview: The Grizzled Young Veterans defend the NXT UK Tag Team Titles in the main event.

episodes.name: May 15, 2019
episodes.overview: Ligero, Jordan Devlin, Wolfgang, and Dave Mastiff look to qualify for the WWE UK Championship No. 1 Contender's Fatal 4-Way Match.

episodes.name: May 22, 2019
episodes.overview: Pete Dunne and WALTER look to exceed expectations in another epic clash for the coveted WWE United Kingdom Championship.

episodes.name: September 17, 2020 - Returns Live
episodes.overview: Live show returns

episodes.name: NXT UK #127
episodes.overview: Piper Niven and Jinny battle to determine the No. 1 Contender to Kay Lee Ray's NXT UK Women's Championship.

episodes.name: NXT UK #128
episodes.overview: NXT UK Champion WALTER puts his title on the line against A-Kid. NXT UK Women's Champion Kay Lee Ray comes face-to-face with Jinny ahead of their title showdown.

episodes.name: NXT UK #129
episodes.overview: NXT UK Women's Champion Kay Lee Ray puts her championship and historic title reign on the line against No. 1 Contender Jinny.

episodes.name: NXT UK #130
episodes.overview: Andrews & Webster, Smith & Carter, The Hunt and Pretty Deadly collide in an NXT UK Tag Team Championship No. 1 Contenders Elimination Four Way Match. Ben Carter is in action following his impressive debut.

episodes.name: NXT UK #131
episodes.overview: Jordan Devlin faces his next challenger in the NXT Cruiserweight Championship Open Challenge. Nina Samuels battles Xia Brookside.

episodes.name: NXT UK #134

episodes.overview: After successfully making the 205-pound weight limit, Trent Seven challenges Jordan Devlin for the NXT Cruiserweight Championship. NXT UK Champion WALTER makes a statement.

episodes.name: NXT UK #139

NXT UK Women's Champion Kay Lee Ray teams with Isla Dawn against Meiko Satomura & Emilia McKenzie. Tyler Bate collides with Noam Dar in an NXT UK Heritage Cup Title No. 1 Contender's Match.
